Unitron:



Continued to stand, llistening to Feline.  He really didn't care what she had 
to say, she was actually starting to irritate him.  Unitron had learned to 
resist the urge to kill a long time ago.  He turned his head to Feline.

"No, I don't have any...cards."

Hearing her question about the bot on the table almost made him sigh of 
annoyance.  "If you do not know, then Zardus didn't find it necessary to 
inform you."
